{
  "texts": [
    "In the following, we review the performance of published works that are compatible with deployment on wearable IoT devices, focusing on the false alarms and sensitivity metrics.",
    "False alarm rates (FP/h) are calculated as 3600 W × (1 -Sp), where W is the observation window (in seconds) and Sp is the reported specificity.",
    "Sayeed et al.",
    "11 and Olokodana et al.",
    "12 present representative examples of seizure detection frameworks based on statistical feature extraction."
  ]
}